desc: USDA Organic Certified Premium Blend, made of carefully selected raw harvested Açaí berries from the deep jungles of the Amazon. 14,000 mg of 100% Pure whole Açai berries per ounce serving. Blended to perfection with other superfood ingredients that create a synergy effect for a healthier you.

layout.text: The acai berry has twice the antioxidant power of wild blueberries and 10 times the antioxidant power of red grapes.
